&lt;p class=&quot;p5&quot;&gt;In this role, you will perform full cycle accounting for assigned DRC entities. In addition to owning the day-to-day accounting and month-end close for the assigned DRC entities, you will independently manage statutory audits and regulatory compliance. You will provide support to field exploration teams and vendors. Since KoBold is a startup company, your role will be dynamic and your role and responsibilities will grow as the company grows. &lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
