&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perform full-cycle accounting and financial reporting.&lt;/strong&gt; Manage end-to-end accounting for assigned DRC entities, including monthly close, reconciliations, and variance analysis. Prepare and review journal entries including payroll, and ensure the integrity of the general ledger on an ongoing basis.&lt;/li&gt;
