&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage external audits and relationships with authorities.&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary point of contact for external auditors (ONEC certified DRC auditors and Holding company auditors in South Africa) and local regulatory bodies for assigned entitie

